---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Get the Letters | Chaos With Clarity"
  description="An occasional letter with thoughts AJ doesn't share on Instagram or YouTube — drafts, behind-the-scenes, and questions still being figured out."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="min-height:100svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:8rem 3rem 5rem;position:relative;background:#f3e8d8;">

    <div style="width:1px;height:4rem;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,#cec5ad);margin-bottom:2.5rem;"></div>

    <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:400;">Stay in the Clarity</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(2.75rem,7vw,6rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:0.75rem;line-height:0.95;">Get the Letters</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#c17f3a;font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Honest notes from the middle of it all.</p>

    <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.9rem;max-width:30rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;">
      Thoughts I don't share on Instagram or YouTube.<br/>
      Drafts. Behind-the-scenes process. Questions I'm still figuring out.<br/>
      No spam. No "daily grind" tips. Just honest notes.
    </p>

    <!-- Email form — Replace action with your Beehiiv embed URL -->
    <form style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;width:100%;max-width:22rem;" action="#" method="post">
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="your@email.com"
        required
        style="background:#e8dcc8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;color:#1a1612;font-size:0.88rem;padding:1rem 1.1rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:300;outline:none;width:100%;"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        style="font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;padding:1rem 1.5rem;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:400;"
      >
        Get the Letters
      </button>
    </form>

    <p style="color:#b8ae9a;font-size:0.75rem;margin-top:1rem;letter-spacing:0.06em;">No spam. Ever. Unsubscribe any time.</p>

    <blockquote style="margin-top:4rem;border-top:1px solid #cec5ad;padding-top:2.5rem;max-width:30rem;">
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.8;">"Save pieces that bother you a little.<br/>They usually have something to show you."</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.7rem;color:#b8ae9a;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0.75rem;">— AJ</p>
    </blockquote>

    <div style="width:1px;height:4rem;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#cec5ad,transparent);margin-top:2.5rem;"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT ARRIVES -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;">

    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
      <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:#cec5ad;"></div>
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7a7260;padding:0 1rem;white-space:nowrap;">What arrives</p>
      <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:#cec5ad;"></div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border:1px solid #cec5ad;margin-bottom:5rem;" class="what-grid">

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-pencil-line" style="font-size:2rem;color:#c17f3a;"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;">Poems</h3>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.9;">
          New poems as they come — raw, unpolished, honest. The kind I'd share with a close friend over chai.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;background:#e8dcc8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-notebook" style="font-size:2rem;color:#7a7260;"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;">Essays & Drafts</h3>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.9;">
          Thoughts I'm still working through. Behind-the-scenes process. Questions I don't share anywhere else.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-fire" style="font-size:2rem;color:#5d6b45;"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;">Circles</h3>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.9;">
          Occasional invites to Chaos Circles — small group conversations for people who want to go deeper than surface.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Poem preview -->
    <div style="max-width:44rem;margin:0 auto;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:3rem 3.5rem;">
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:0.75rem;font-weight:400;">A taste</p>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:#1a1612;margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:500;">Let Me Be Conscious</h3>
      <p style="color:#b8ae9a;font-size:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;letter-spacing:0.06em;">2025</p>
      <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:2.2;border-left:2px solid #cec5ad;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
        <p>Let me breathe today, let me be conscious,</p>
        <p>Let me be free today, let me be outrageous,</p>
        <p>Let me feel the pain I keep hiding,</p>
        <p>Let me kiss a plant today I keep avoiding.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/writings" style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
        Read all writings <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .what-grid > div { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #cec5ad; }
    .what-grid > div:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }
</style>
